						<summary>

						<p>This records another gift of a lamp by reclamation of 600 <hi rend="italic">kuḻi</hi> or 6 <hi rend="italic">mā</hi> of land by Śēkkiḻāṉ Ammaiyappaṉ Parāntakadēvaṉ <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Karikālaśōḻa Pallavarāyaṉ of Kuṉṟattūr in Kuṉṟattūr-nāḍu a division of Puliyūr-kōṭṭam <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Kulōttuṅgaśōḻavaḷanāḍu in Jayangoṇḍaśōḻamaṇḍalam.</p>						

