<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrīḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> ja</hi>yaṅkoṇṭacoḻamaṇṭalattup puliyūrkoṭṭamāna kulot tuṅkacoḻavaḷanāṭṭu kuṉṟattūrnāṭṭu
<lb n="2"/>kuṉṟattūr cekkiḻān Ammaiappan <unclear>parā</unclear>ntakatevanāna karikālacoḻap pallavaraiyaṉ <hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>yaṅkoṇṭa coḻavaḷanāṭṭu Āk—
<lb n="3"/>kūrnāṭṭut tirukkaṭavūr Uṭaiyār <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>kālakālatevar koyilil tiripuvanac cakkaravattikaḷ <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>kulottuṅka coḻatevaṟku yā—
<lb n="4"/>ṇṭu nālāvatu mutal Erikiṟa tirununtāviḷakku cantirātittavaṟ cella Ittevar tevatāṉam Erukkāṭṭucceriyil maṇaṟkunṟu kalli
<lb n="5" break="no"/>yum kaḻitūr<supplied reason="omitted">r</supplied>ttu<supplied reason="omitted">m</supplied> tiruttina nilam Āṟu mā<unclear>vu</unclear>kku Ikkoyilil Eriyum tirununtāviḷakku Oṉṟu <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g><g ref="sym:dash-long" type="punctuation">.</g>
